        "content": "<p>It seems that mathlib3 has same element order in right coset, but mathlib4 not</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/group_theory/coset.html\">https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/group_theory/coset.html</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/GroupTheory/Coset/Basic.html\">https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/GroupTheory/Coset/Basic.html</a></p>",
